'''Synthdroids''' were a type of [[Droid/Legends|droid]] created by [[Loronar Corporation/Legends|Loronar Corporation]] and launched in [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]].<ref name="TEGtD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref> They used sculpted [[Synthskin/Legends|synthskin]] over metal armatures to resemble [[Human/Legends|Humans]] or other lifeforms. In this respect they were similar to [[Human replica droid]]s. However, unlike Human replica droids, synthdroids used [[Centrally Controlled Independent Replicant|CCIR]] technology, allowing them to be controlled from a central location and to contain minimal internal computers.

Loronar stressed the benefits of synthdroids including aesthetic quality, reliability, high performance standards and immunity to viruses. However, the CCIR technology made them expensive.

Synthdroids could be found in pleasure domes on [[Hesperidium/Legends|Hesperidium]] and [[Carosi XII]], where they were quite popular.<ref name="TEGtD" />

